{"tid":508603,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"越接近平安夜既凌晨，脫脫就越發強大！","createTime":"2017-12-24T12:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T21:45:42.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5495e12ee95cad710fa95f3f7decbb146333758","tid":508603,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"脫脫係銅鑼灣滿街情侶既道路上如入無之境，行如流水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n視線中穿插衣着惹火少女既身影，佢地明顯既股溝同乳溝沒有保留地置於我正前方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地用下流既身體緊密貼係於男伴身上套弄&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係！<br />\n脫脫不可思議地冷靜，穩如泰山！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對住多如繁星既閃光彈連環暴風，我輕輕地係心中默念：無打打<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n展開時空結界同進行向量操作，不痛不癢，沒有傷到脫脫分毫！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n脫脫亦都對滿地狗糧，可以飽食餐頓無動於衷，成就仙人聖者既出世境界<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呼吸沒有被打亂，就咁拂袖孤身踏上歸去道路&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此刻又再強了幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fb0ee2ead59f11a5ec08c118ea3306e394b36a","tid":508603,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:57:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e11e1a2d9326a8cbc5e8dfd22415aca49db4c38f","tid":508603,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂！"},{"pid":"2edf6c1fc5adfa84251115cf6508e010a0d6f2bf","tid":508603,"uid":32150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T15:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1de82cd3903f88889b183b59253d999adc7619","tid":508603,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />